    "body" : "<p><code>dateString.split(\"[/]\");</code> gives you the array of string. <code>split()</code> function take input in <code>regex</code> thats why <code>\"[]\"</code> are added. </p>\n\n<p>if the dateString is \"dd/mm/yy\" then <code>dateString.split(\"[/]\")</code> return the <code>String</code> array consists of <code>{\"dd\",\"mm\",\"yy\"}</code>.</p>\n"
